	M	utils/src/test/java/org/apache/felix/utils/properties/TypedPropertiesTest.java&lt;br/&gt;
Committed r1807697&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16526063" author="kwin" created="Thu, 28 Jun 2018 07:55:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is the &lt;tt&gt;ConfigurationHandler&lt;/tt&gt; within &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/felix/blob/trunk/configadmin/src/main/java/org/apache/felix/cm/file/ConfigurationHandler.java&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/felix/blob/trunk/configadmin/src/main/java/org/apache/felix/cm/file/ConfigurationHandler.java&lt;/a&gt; now no longer in use? Because that one has not been touched. Should it be deprecated?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16526093" author="gnt" created="Thu, 28 Jun 2018 08:24:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s a fork.&lt;br/&gt;
The usage is slightly different, because FileInstall exposes those files while ConfigAdmin keep them internal.&lt;br/&gt;
Please raise a new JIRA issue for ConfigAdmin if you want to have some changes there.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
